          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In Bi-209(n,2n)Bi-208 reactions, the neutron spectra of",
                "1st and 2nd neutron-emissions were assumed to be fitted",
                "with the constant-temperature type formula,",
                "  A * E * (exp(-E/T)),",
                "after correcting for the detector efficiency.  E, T and",
                "A are kinetic energy of the neutron,nuclear temperature",
                "and normalization constant, respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MISC-COL": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MISC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "   Nuclear temperature for the evaporation of",
                "2nd neutrons."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The ratio of the number from the first to the second",
                "neutron in the Bi-209(n,2n) process is,",
                "      1.06 +- 0.15.",
                "and this indicates that the role of the gamma",
                "de-excitation proved to be negligible."
              ]
            }
          ],
